book
------------------------------------------------
+ id
+ title
+ author
+ isbn
+ etc.
------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------
customer
------------------------------------------------
+ id
+ first_name
+ first_name
+ email
+ address
+ city
+ state
+ zip
+ etc.
------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------
book_copy
------------------------------------------------
+ id
+ book_id (FK to book)
+ customer_id (FK to customer)
+ checked_out
+ due_date
+ etc.
